{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"3689c451-d011-43e8-ac88-84a5bfcc24de","content":"The directory doesn't exist yet, but I can tell you exactly what to configure to publish a C# MCP server as a **dotnet tool** on NuGet.org:\n\n### Required `.csproj` properties\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n  <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n\n  <!-- These make it a dotnet tool -->\n  <PackAsTool>true</PackAsTool>\n  <ToolCommandName>my-mcp-server</ToolCommandName>\n\n  <!-- NuGet metadata (required for nuget.org) -->\n  <PackageId>MyMcpServer</PackageId>\n  <Version>1.0.0</Version>\n  <Authors>YourName</Authors>\n  <Description>An MCP server for ...</Description>\n  <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>\n  <PackageReadmeFile>README.md</PackageReadmeFile>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### Key steps\n\n1. **`PackAsTool = true`** — this is the critical property that makes `dotnet pack` produce a tool package.\n2. **`ToolCommandName`** — the CLI command users will run (e.g., `my-mcp-server`).\n3. **Pack it:** `dotnet pack -c Release`\n4. **Push it:** `dotnet nuget push bin/Release/MyMcpServer.1.0.0.nupkg --api-key YOUR_KEY --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json`\n\n### Users install & run it with\n\n```bash\ndotnet tool install -g MyMcpServer\nmy-mcp-server          # runs via stdio\n```\n\n### MCP client config (e.g., VS Code)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"my-server\": {\n      \"command\": \"my-mcp-server\",\n      \"args\": [],\n      \"transportType\": \"stdio\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nThe two essential things are **`PackAsTool`** and **`ToolCommandName`** — everything else is standard NuGet metadata. Since your server uses stdio transport, it works naturally as a dotnet tool with no additional transport configuration needed.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"aac8d551-8224-44a5-9e5d-9bac3336e85e","outputTokens":559,"requestId":"8447:24F978:10463FB:1455F0E:69FFDB47"},"id":"68c4b723-e60a-4e02-a1a5-936b987e7a7a","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:11:46.883Z","parentId":"9333be63-2623-42eb-b046-8a4cefaafa54"}
